{"title":"题洪秀全故居","authors":["洪三泰"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":8,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"题洪秀全故居"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪三泰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山还蒙着浓重的王气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水飞溅着二十世纪的风流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那棵神奇的龙眼树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疯长成龙的形象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"私塾里响起了多国语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断垣上站立过当今伟人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风水宝地旅游胜地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聚集着龙骧虎步的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天王早已远遁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下的是血与火的伤痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也留着土地无声的誓言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当拜金梦在有人心中燃起火焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我你他同时把青春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留在这圣洁的山水之间"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}